<section id="solutions" class="section">
    <h2>Our Solutions</h2>
    <p>The AgroWorm System transforms organic waste into high-protein worms and nutrient-rich compost, offering a scalable, low-cost solution for sustainable agriculture.</p>
    <p>We provide:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Starter kits for worm farming</li>
        <li>Training programs and workshops</li>
        <li>Community-based composting solutions</li>
    </ul>
</section>

